Package: glantank-utils
Architecture: arm armel
Depends: devio
Description: utilities for the GLAN Tank
 The GLAN Tank is a Network Attached Storage (NAS) device based on an
 Intel IOP CPU.  This package contains a script for this device which
 makes sure that the kernel is made bootable after a new kernel
 installation or upgrade.

Package: glantank-installer
Section: debian-installer
Priority: standard
XC-Package-Type: udeb
Architecture: arm armel
XB-Subarchitecture: iop32x
Provides: bootable-system
Depends: cdebconf-udeb, kernel-installer, archdetect
XB-Installer-Menu-Item: 73
Description: Make GLAN Tank bootable
 This package will install scripts to make the GLAN Tank bootable.

